headline: Franklin Templeton Announces Plan to Liquidate ClearBridge Sustainable Infrastructure ETF
summary: SAN MATEO, Calif., December 05, 2025--Franklin Templeton today announced it will liquidate and dissolve ClearBridge Sustainable Infrastructure ETF (INFR). The liquidation is anticipated to occur on or about January 29, 2026. The liquidation was approved by the Fund’s board of trustees on December 4, 2025.

headline: Webster's Arm Acquires SecureSave: A Smart Bet on Future Growth?
summary: Will HSA Bank's acquisition of SecureSave help WBS boost growth by adding employer emergency-savings accounts to its financial-wellness suite? Let us find out.
